      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped spinach</strong> and<strong> halved tomatoes</strong> to the <strong>orzo</strong> with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>torn</strong> <strong>basil leaves </strong>(save the rest for later!) and cook until the spinach has wilted</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spinach & tomato orzo</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
